rprise, has worked with U.S. Steel in an effort to assuage the concerns about the merger raised by politicians and labor groups.", "score": 0.45653152, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://www.france24.com/en/tv-shows/business/20250106-nippon-steel-and-us-steel-sue-biden-administration-usw-and-cleveland-cliffs-over-blocked-merger-deal", "title": "Nippon Steel, US Steel sue Biden administration over blocked merger deal - Business - France 24", "content": "US Steel and Nippon Steel have filed lawsuits in Washington in a bid to overturn last week\'s decision by the Biden administration to block their planned merger. In a scathing statement, the steelmakers accused the outgoing president of making the move for political gain. They also sued the USW union and rival bidder Cleveland-Cliffs, accusing them of colluding to kill the deal to try to monopolise the US steel industry. Also in this edition: a 276 kg bluefin tuna fetches \\u20ac1.2 million at a New", "score": 0.41606155, "raw_content": null}]',
